orbitSensitivity.title: Orbit Sensitivity
orbitSensitivity.description: How fast the camera moves around the orbit. Higher is faster

distanceSensitivity.title: Distance Sensitivity
distanceSensitivity.description: How fast the camera moves in and out. Higher is faster

distanceMax.title: Distance Max
distanceMax.description: Setting this at 0 will give an infinite distance limit

inertiaFactor.title: Inertia Factor
inertiaFactor.description: Higher value means that the camera will continue moving after the user has stopped dragging. 0 is fully responsive.

focusEntity.title: Focus Entity
focusEntity.description: Entity for the camera to focus on. If blank, then the camera will use the whole scene

frameOnStart.title: Frame on Start
frameOnStart.description: Frames the entity or scene at the start of the application."

childOfActualEntity.title: Child Of Actual Entity
childOfActualEntity.description: Tick if the shape is a child of the actual entity object

keepUpdating.title: Keep Updating
keepUpdating.description: Update the shape data every frame (only toggle if the entity moves as can be expensive)

orbitSensitivity.title: Orbit Sensitivity
orbitSensitivity.description: How fast the camera moves around the orbit. Higher is faster

distanceSensitivity.title: Distance Sensitivity
distanceSensitivity.description: How fast the camera moves in and out. Higher is faster

clipPlaneChunk.title: Clip Plane Shader
clipPlaneChunk.description: Shader that implements clip plane logic

camera.title: Camera
camera.description: The camera controlled by this first person view. It should be a child of the entity to which this script is assigned. If no camera is assigned, the script will create one for you.

deadZone.title: Dead Zone
deadZone.description: Radial thickness of inner dead zone of the virtual joysticks. This dead zone ensures the virtual joysticks report a value of 0 even if a touch deviates a small amount from the initial touch.

turnSpeed.title: Turn Speed
turnSpeed.description: Maximum turn speed in degrees per second

radius.title: Radius
radius.description: The radius of the virtual joystick in CSS pixels.

doubleTapInterval.title: Double Tap Interval
doubleTapInterval.description: The time in milliseconds between two taps of the right virtual joystick for a double tap to register. A double tap will trigger a jump.

deadZoneLow.title: Low Dead Zone
deadZoneLow.description: Radial thickness of inner dead zone of pad's joysticks. This dead zone ensures that all pads report a value of 0 for each joystick axis when untouched.

deadZoneHigh.title: High Dead Zone
deadZoneHigh.description: Radial thickness of outer dead zone of pad's joysticks. This dead zone ensures that all pads can reach the -1 and 1 limits of each joystick axis.

turnSpeed.title: Turn Speed
turnSpeed.description: Maximum turn speed in degrees per second

camera.description: Optional, assign a camera entity, otherwise one is created
